## Key Features by Section

### A. Device Configuration (`/configurations/devices`)
- **4 Tabs**: Device Types · Device Profiles · Assignment Rules · Firmware & OTA
- Add/Edit Device Types with capability checkboxes (CAN Bus, Fuel, Dashcam, etc.)
- Device Profiles: reporting intervals, transmission mode (TCP/UDP/HTTP/MQTT), APN, precision
- Auto-assignment rules by IMEI/Serial pattern with wildcard support
- Firmware OTA toggle per version with rollout groups (alpha/beta/stable)

### B. Event & Alert Configuration (`/configurations/events`)
- **Event Rule Builder** with threshold, duration, day/time filter, severity, escalation
- 🧪 **"Test Configuration"** button — fires mock alert and shows success banner
- **Notification Channels** tab — Email, SMS, In-App, Webhook, Push with enable/disable toggles
- **Alert Routing** table — role and department-based escalation chains

### C. Geofence Management (`/configurations/geofences`)
- Create circle (lat/lng/radius), polygon, or route-based geofences
- Trigger config: Entry, Exit, Dwell (with dwell time field)
- KML / GeoJSON file import tab

### D. Maintenance & Service Rules (`/configurations/maintenance`)
- Mileage / Engine Hours / Date-based rule triggers
- Configurable reminder threshold, workshop assignment
- Auto Job Card generation toggle

### E. Data & Telemetry (`/configurations/telemetry`)
- Data retention period + raw/processed data toggles
- **Fuel Calibration Table** — editable Voltage→Liters mapping
- **Custom I/O Mapping** — add/remove digital/analog pin→event mappings
- CAN Data Parsing — DBC file upload, ECU type, baud rate

### F. User Permissions (`/configurations/permissions`)
- Custom role creation with visual permission picker (grouped by resource)
- **Permission Matrix** — side-by-side role comparison view
- **Vehicle Group Visibility** — toggle per role / per fleet group

### G. Integration Settings (`/configurations/integrations`)
- **API Key management** — generate with scoped permissions, revoke
- **Webhooks** — add, test (mock success response), event subscriptions
- **Third-Party Integrations** — connect/disconnect cards (SAP ERP, Fuel Card, Insurance, Wialon)
- **MQTT Broker** — host, port, TLS, client ID, topic pattern + test button

### H. Branding & Localization (`/configurations/branding`)
- Company name, logo upload with live preview
- Primary brand color picker
- Timezone, language, distance & fuel unit selectors
- Report header/footer with **live preview panel**

